<h1>New Post</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <p>Guidelines for new posts:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Include your full name, height, and cable service provider.</li>
      <li>Confirm whether you have ever, or have never, felt like a plastic bag.</li>
      <li>Show enthusiasm <i>without</i> using exclamation points aggressively.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
  <%= render partial: 'form', locals: {topic: @topic, post: @post} %>
  </div>
</div>
